The paper discusses the use of data structures and algorithms for efficient file matching, which falls under the categories of data structures (cs.DS), cryptography and security (cs.CR), information retrieval (cs.IR), databases (cs.DB), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV). However, since the focus is on data structures and algorithms, cs.DS is the most likely category, followed by cs.CR and cs.IR.
